---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Hey, I'm Ethan"
	description="Why I started Eco Living Journey (and why you don't need to be rich to be sustainable)."
	pubDate={new Date('February 26 2026')}
>
	
	<img src="/ethan.jpg" alt="Ethan from Eco Living Journey" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px;" />

	<h2>Hi, I'm Ethan. I thought going green was only for rich people.</h2>
	
	<p>
		If you look at Instagram or big magazines, sustainable living looks like a luxury aesthetic. It's all $100 organic cotton shirts, high-end solar panels, and perfectly matching glass pantry jars.
	</p>
	</Layout>